#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:1
msgid "Trainer Duties and Agreement"
msgstr "Responsabilidades y Trainer Agreement"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:3
msgid ""
"As of May 2017, the Trainers group adopted a Trainer Agreement outlining "
"Trainer duties. Only active Trainers are voting members of the Trainer "
"community. An inactive Trainer may re-activate their Trainer status at any "
"time by resuming Trainer activities."
msgstr ""
"A partir de mayo de 2017, el grupo de Trainers adoptó un Acuerdo (Trainer "
"Agreement) que describe las responsabilidades del Trainer. Solo los Trainers"
" activos son miembros votantes de la comunidad de Trainers. Un Trainer "
"inactivo puede reactivar su estado de Trainer en cualquier momento "
"reanudando las actividades del Trainer."

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:5
msgid "Trainer Agreement"
msgstr "Trainer Agreement"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:7
msgid ""
"I agree to follow the Code of Conduct (CoC) in all communications and "
"interactions with The Carpentries community and to promptly report any "
"violations of the CoC that I become aware of."
msgstr ""
"Estoy de acuerdo en seguir el Código de Conducta (CoC) en todas las "
"comunicaciones e interacciones con la comunidad de The Carpentries y en "
"informar de inmediato cualquier violación del CoC de la que tenga "
"conocimiento."

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:9
msgid ""
"I understand that the secondary learning outcomes of workshops are as "
"important as their stated goals. I will:"
msgstr ""
"Entiendo que los resultados del aprendizaje secundario de los talleres son "
"tan importantes como sus objetivos establecidos. Voy a:"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:10
msgid ""
"Communicate The Carpentries community values to trainees and model that "
"behaviour myself in how I teach"
msgstr ""
"Comunicar los valores de la comunidad de The Carpentries a trainees y "
"modelar ese comportamiento en la forma en que enseño"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:11
msgid "Provide a welcoming and supporting environment for trainees"
msgstr "Proporcionar un ambiente acogedor y de apoyo para las trainees."

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:12
msgid "Model our “show, don’t tell” policy in instructor training"
msgstr ""
"Modelar nuestra política de \"mostrar, no decir\" durante el instructor "
"training"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:13
msgid ""
"Connect the principles used in The Carpentries workshops with other teaching"
" contexts"
msgstr ""
"Conectar los principios utilizados en los talleres de The Carpentries con "
"otros contextos de enseñanza."

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:15
msgid ""
"I understand that it is important to keep up to date and in touch with the "
"Trainer community so that my teaching will reflect current practices and "
"curriculum. Therefore, to be an active Trainer, I agree to:"
msgstr ""
"Entiendo que es importante mantenerme al día y en contacto con la comunidad "
"de Trainers para que mi enseñanza refleje las prácticas y el plan de "
"estudios actuales. Por lo tanto, para ser un Trainer activo, acepto:"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:16
msgid "Teach at least two instructor training events per year"
msgstr "Brindar al menos dos instructor trainings por año"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:17
msgid "Host on average four teaching demonstrations per year  (1 per quarter)"
msgstr ""
"Organizar en promedio cuatro demostraciones de enseñanza por año (una por "
"trimestre)"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:18
msgid ""
"Regularly attend Trainer meetings when possible and read meeting "
"minutes/notes when I am not able to attend"
msgstr ""
"Asistir regularmente a las meetings de Trainers cuando sea posible y leer "
"las minutas/notas de la reunión cuando no sea posible asistir"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:19
msgid "Read emails sent to the Trainer listserv"
msgstr "Leer emails enviados a la lista de distribución de Trainers"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:20
msgid "Keep up-to-date with the instructor training curriculum"
msgstr "Mantenerme al día con la currícula del instructor training"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:21
msgid ""
"Teach a curriculum that fulfills all of the current requirements for "
"instructor certification"
msgstr ""
"Enseñe una currícula que cumpla con todos los requisitos actuales para la "
"certificación de instructor"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:22
msgid ""
"Provide feedback to other trainers and Carpentries staff about training "
"events to help continue developing our offerings"
msgstr ""
"Proporcionar comentarios a otros trainers y al personal de las Carpentries "
"sobre eventos de training para ayudar a continuar desarrollando nuestras "
"ofertas"

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/instructor_training/duties_agreement.md:24
msgid ""
"I understand that The Carpentries staff need an accurate understanding of "
"Trainer availability in order to plan instructor training events. If at any "
"point I am no longer able to serve as a Trainer, I will let The Carpentries "
"staff know. I understand that only active Trainers are voting members of the"
" Trainer community, but that I will be able to re-activate my Trainer status"
" at any time by resuming Trainer activities."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo que el personal de The Carpentries necesita una comprensión precisa"
" de la disponibilidad del Trainer para planificar eventos de onstructor "
"training. Si en algún momento ya no puedo servir como Trainer, informaré al "
"personal de The Carpentries. Entiendo que solo los Trainers activos son "
"miembros votantes de la comunidad de Trainers, pero que podré reactivar mi "
"estado de Trainer en cualquier momento reanudando las actividades del "
"Trainer."
